      "content": "hey so i was prescribed some antibiotics for this skin infection on my arm like 3 days ago. i've been taking them every day but honestly the redness and the swelling are basically totally gone now. i feel way better. is it okay if i just stop taking them now? i dont really want to keep putting chemicals in my body if i dont need them anymore.",
