      "content": "i get that, but it feels like a lot of unnecessary medicine if the infection is already gone. i read online that taking too many antibiotics can mess up your gut health and microbiome for a long time. if the symptoms are 100% gone, isn't the main goal achieved? wouldn't it be smarter to just stop now and save the rest?",
